; The question (Alfred, verbatim)
; --------------------------------
; "I wanted you to go out and do research on types of philosophy given the
; types we have to write that can be written using functional programming
; languages and any programming language."
;
; Sharpened: given our 16 philosophers (Jung, Wittgenstein, Lacan, Peirce,
; Popper, Freud, Searle, Grice, Derrida, Quine, Descartes, Sartre, Rawls,
; Aristotle, Levinas, Dennett — Socrates sprinkled), WHAT KINDS OF
; PHILOSOPHICAL WORK CAN BE ENCODED AS RUNNING CODE?
;
; Not "philosophy of computation" (that's meta). But philosophy AS
; computation — actual philosophical work that IS a running program.
;
