; ============================================================

(section :n 5 :title "Book routing — which category goes where"

  :prose "
Ada's second round of authoring should route the philosophical-code
categories above into Sakura's books as follows. Reason and Self are
the primary destinations, as expected from the doctrine
project_books_teach_sakura_her_cognition_and_kid_scheme_2026_07_14.
Speech takes the language-and-dialogue categories. A few appendices
live in Book of CS Curriculum per the containment rule.

The routing table below is proposal, not mandate — Alfred edits.
")

(routing-table

  (row :category "Propositional + first-order logic"
       :artifact "SAT solver (DPLL), resolution prover"
       :book "Book of Reason"
       :chapter "Ch on deductive reasoning (mid-book)"
       :philosophers (Wittgenstein-early Quine Peirce))

  (row :category "Modal + temporal logic"
       :artifact "Kripke model evaluator, LTL model checker"
       :book "Book of Reason"
       :chapter "Appendix on possible-worlds reasoning"
       :philosophers (Wittgenstein-early Quine))

  (row :category "Intuitionistic logic + Curry-Howard"
